latestIgtvVideos.title: Ghar More Pardesiya(Performance)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ever since I was a kid, I had an extreme inclination towards singing and dancing.
I first enrolled in a dancing class when I was six. I remember liking it a lot and willing to make efforts to progress. But then due to a series of unfortunate circumstances, I had to call it quits and I have regretted that decision ever since until now.
Life kept moving and everything changed so drastically for me that I couldnt rekindle my passion for dancing. So finally this pandemic got me some time to think about the things i have missed in life and being not able to dance was the first thing that came to my mind.
I called Ashish sir and immediately began training like the six year old Tanya i used to be.
Same Passion, Same Desire.
Dance is an indescribable feeling for me.
I  love dance, because when I dance I become free. I can express myself at my best. When I dance I forget everything else - problems, stress, whatever that is in my head. I just have fun, express myself and enjoy the moment!
As soon as I got finished with the classes I wanted to share it with everyone I love and so I decided to make this video for all of you.
It took a great deal of courage and I had to convince myself over and over again to post this one online but I don't want any regrets in my life. The biggest poison is REGRET.
We have got one life and life is too short to wake up with regrets.
So I am sharing this with all of you and I hope you all love it as much as I did and I just want to tell each and everyone that its never too late to pursue your dreams as I have finally accomplished my childhood dream today.
Videography: @n29_photography
Choreography: @inspire_dance_studio .
